this is the education platform where the AI tutor will handle add responsibilities of a parent and help in learning the students easily using AI tools
motive of this tool is giving full guidance to your children, What's happening in the world how can your child become updated, not feel the deficiency of guidance even their parent are not capable to tell them about a particular field. Making them resourceful. App will analyze your students record and give guides that in which field your student is outperforming and based on that basis the app will guide the student and let them become the master of that field as well as with the success in other fields.
